      <title>OPEC+ 推迟恢复产量后，沙特阿拉伯下调油价</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-08/saudi-arabia-cuts-oil-prices-after-opec-delays-reviving-output</link>
